400
00:31:50,761 --> 00:31:53,261
...dalam pasukan Amerika
dengan daya yang tak diketahui.

401
00:31:53,778 --> 00:31:54,978
Di mana lokasinya?

402
00:31:55,452 --> 00:31:56,986
Area Jentera Charlevaux.

403
00:31:57,837 --> 00:31:59,637
Apa mereka berusaha mundur?

404
00:32:00,294 --> 00:32:02,227
